oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Service medal and lapel pin of Pvt. Henry E. Phillips
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This is a 2005 replacement Victory Medal that was requested by the family of Pvt. Henry E. Phillips. An American Legion membership lapel pin accompanies the medal. Phillips, who never saw combat, was from Oliver Springs, Tennessee. Oliver Springs sits at the junction of Roane, Anderson and Morgan Counties.
